To install this chart drawing application on your server you need perform following steps:

1) Install Yii2. As an option, you can install Yii by running the following commands under a Web-accessible folder :
composer global require "fxp/composer-asset-plugin:^1.2.0"
composer create-project --prefer-dist yiisoft/yii2-app-basic basic

If you do not already have Composer installed, run the following commands:
curl -sS https://getcomposer.org/installer | php
mv composer.phar /usr/local/bin/composer 

You may also install Yii2 from archive http://www.yiiframework.com/download/

2) Install Google Chart extension. The preferred way to install this extension is through composer:
composer require scotthuangzl/yii2-google-chart "dev-master"

3) Replace folders in you just created project with corresponding folders from repo.  

4) Create database using dump file base.sql 

5) Adjust you database settings for actual  in /config/db.php

6) Site is ready for use!

 
